parameters: Old Man: "Ugh... It's cold... It's scary... I'm frozen stiff here..."

Old Man: "In such a scary and cold place, I doubt even a sweet and
sour pork bento stall would come... Even though it's written in the
gourmet book... Ahh, ahh... I'm so hungry."
Old Man: "Oh! You guys are... from that time...!"
Old Man: "Is that so... You're going to pass away..."
Old Man: "No, I mean... You're going to leave this place..."

Old Man: "Going to such a scary-looking place, you should reconsider.
It's like barging into a mafia office. I'm so scared, I'm just frozen
in place here... Ugh."

Old Man: "Is that so. You're still going, huh? I guess it's futile to
stop you."
You've obtained the "Robe of the Dark Night."

Old Man: "This robe has incredible defense. And it greatly enhances
your abilities. My black robe is made from the same material."

Old Man: "After all, my only strengths are my quick escape and wearing
amazing armor. That's how I've managed to survive here... Teehee!"

Old Man: Once the battle is over, I'll make a run for it~. My legs are
shaking so much I'm frozen in place right here~... Yo-yo-yo...

Old Man: But if possible, I don't want you guys to go... no, I mean, I
don't want you to leave...
